---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es" class="dark scroll-smooth">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title={`Sobre mí - ${SITE_TITLE}`}
			description="Kamerr Ezz: desarrollador full-stack y emprendedor creativo. Builder-educator: construye productos reales y convierte el proceso en educación práctica. Zeew Space, transparencia operativa y aprendizaje aplicado."
		/>
	</head>
	
	<body class="bg-[#050505] text-[#FAFAFA] font-sans selection:bg-[#d5338b] selection:text-white" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 32px 32px;">
		
		<div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto min-h-screen border-x-[1.5px] border-white/10 bg-[#0A0A0A]/90 backdrop-blur-md flex flex-col shadow-[0_0_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.9)]">
			
			{/* ── TOP NAV ── */}
			<nav class="flex items-stretch border-b-[1.5px] border-white/10 sticky top-0 z-50 bg-[#0A0A0A] h-14">
				<a href="/" class="flex items-center px-4 md:px-8 font-mono text-[11px] md:text-sm font-black tracking-widest uppercase text-zinc-500 transition-colors hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10 border-r-[1.5px] border-white/10 w-max shrink-0">
					<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-zinc-600 mr-2 transition-colors group-hover:bg-white"></span>
					KamerrEzz
				</a>
				<div class="flex-1 flex justify-end">
					<a href="/projects" class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center px-6 font-mono text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-zinc-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 border-l-[1.5px] border-white/10 transition-colors">
						Proyectos
					</a>
					<a href="/blog" class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center px-6 font-mono text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-zinc-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 border-l-[1.5px] border-white/10 transition-colors">
						Blog
					</a>
					<div class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center px-6 font-mono text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-white bg-white/5 border-l-[1.5px] border-white/10 transition-colors">
						<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#d5338b] mr-2 shadow-[0_0_8px_#d5338b]"></span>
						Sobre mí
					</div>
					<a href="https://github.com/KamerrEzz" target="_blank" class="flex sm:hidden lg:flex items-center justify-center px-4 md:px-6 font-mono text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-zinc-400 hover:text-[#d5338b] hover:bg-[#d5338b]/10 border-l-[1.5px] border-white/10 transition-all">
						GitHub ↗
					</a>
				</div>
			</nav>

			{/* ── MAIN CONTENT ── */}
			<main class="flex-1 flex flex-col">
				
				{/* PAGE HEADER */}
				<header class="p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-20 border-b-[1.5px] border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden group">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/[0.02] to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
					
					<div class="mb-4">
						<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#FAFF00] text-black shadow-[3px_3px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)] font-mono text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest">
							Identidad ///
						</span>
					</div>

					<h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter text-[#FAFAFA] mb-6">
						SOBRE <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-zinc-400 to-[#d5338b]">MÍ.</span>
					</h1>
					
					<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-light">
						Desarrollador full-stack y emprendedor creativo. De la misma forma en que el código estructura sistemas, uso el software para diseñar herramientas educativas funcionales.
					</p>
				</header>

				{/* CONTENT SECTIONS GRID */}
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 divide-y-[1.5px] lg:divide-y-0 lg:divide-x-[1.5px] divide-white/10 border-b-[1.5px] border-white/10">
					
					{/* LEFT COLUMN: Main Info */}
					<div class="lg:col-span-8 flex flex-col divide-y-[1.5px] divide-white/10 bg-[#0C0C0C]">
						
						{/* Intro Section */}
						<section class="p-8 md:p-12 hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors relative group">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
								<div class="w-10 h-10 border-[1.5px] border-[#d5338b] bg-[#d5338b]/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#d5338b]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path></svg>
								</div>
								<h2 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white">Filosofía Operativa</h2>
							</div>
							
							<div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed font-light">
								<p>
									Mi identidad se resume en <strong class="text-white font-bold">builder-educator</strong>: mentalidad de producto con corazón de maestro. Construyo productos reales y convierto ese proceso en educación práctica — desde la idea hasta la ejecución, sin ocultar iteraciones, fallos ni decisiones técnicas.
								</p>
								<p>
									La promesa corporativa es la <strong class="text-white font-bold">transparencia operativa</strong>: no hay "secretos", hay procesos. Si algo no funciona, lo desarmo hasta entenderlo y luego lo explico con claridad. No comparto solo resultados: muestro decisiones, errores y correcciones para que otros aprendan a <span class="text-[#d5338b]">pensar sistemas, no solo a usar herramientas.</span>
								</p>
								<p class="text-zinc-400">
									Mi autoridad no viene de títulos, sino de evidencia pública, coherencia y persistencia documentando proyectos y aprendizaje aplicado.
								</p>
							</div>

							<div class="mt-8">
								<a href="/blog/quien-es-kamerr-ezz/" class="inline-flex items-center text-[#d5338b] hover:text-white font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] border-b-[1.5px] border-[#d5338b] hover:border-white pb-1 transition-all">
									Leer manifiesto completo →
								</a>
							</div>
						</section>

						{/* Experience Section */}
						<section class="p-8 md:p-12 hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors relative group">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-10">
								<div class="w-10 h-10 border-[1.5px] border-[#FAFF00] bg-[#FAFF00]/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FAFF00]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path></svg>
								</div>
								<h2 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white">Línea de Tiempo</h2>
							</div>

							<div class="space-y-8 relative before:absolute before:inset-0 before:ml-2 before:-translate-x-px md:before:mx-auto md:before:translate-x-0 before:h-full before:w-[1.5px] before:bg-gradient-to-b before:from-white/20 before:to-transparent">
								
								{/* Exp Item */}
								<div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group is-active">
									<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full border-[1.5px] border-[#d5338b] bg-[#111] shadow-[0_0_10px_#d5338b] text-slate-500 group-[.is-active]:text-emerald-50 shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 z-10"></div>
									<div class="w-[calc(100%-2.5rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-1.5rem)] p-6 border-[1.5px] border-white/10 bg-[#0A0A0A] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform group-hover:border-white/20">
										<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
											<span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 tracking-widest uppercase">2023 - Presente</span>
										</div>
										<h3 class="font-bold text-white text-xl mb-1">Zeew Space</h3>
										<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Ecosistema educativo con el eslogan "Un espacio para aprender". Cursos convertidos en proyectos reales, práctica desde el primer día rompiendo el ciclo de la educación tradicional.</p>
									</div>
								</div>

								{/* Exp Item */}
								<div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group">
									<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full border-[1.5px] border-white/20 bg-[#111] shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 z-10"></div>
									<div class="w-[calc(100%-2.5rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-1.5rem)] p-6 border-[1.5px] border-white/10 bg-[#0A0A0A] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform group-hover:border-white/20">
										<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
											<span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 tracking-widest uppercase">2022 - 2024</span>
										</div>
										<h3 class="font-bold text-white text-xl mb-1">Pivotes Base</h3>
										<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Experimentación con modelos de producto. Zeew Space funciona como prueba y extensión de la marca: mi manera de aprender y enseñar son la misma en la práctica.</p>
									</div>
								</div>

								{/* Exp Item */}
								<div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group">
									<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full border-[1.5px] border-white/20 bg-[#111] shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 z-10"></div>
									<div class="w-[calc(100%-2.5rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-1.5rem)] p-6 border-[1.5px] border-white/10 bg-[#0A0A0A] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform group-hover:border-white/20">
										<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
											<span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 tracking-widest uppercase">2016 - 2022</span>
										</div>
										<h3 class="font-bold text-white text-xl mb-1">Fundamentos</h3>
										<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Creación de contenido bajo KsGrapin; Zeew API (REST). Desarrollo de herramientas internas, aprendizaje forzado de frontend y arquitectura.</p>
									</div>
								</div>

							</div>
						</section>
					</div>

					{/* RIGHT COLUMN: Sidebar Stats & Pillars */}
					<div class="lg:col-span-4 flex flex-col divide-y-[1.5px] divide-white/10 bg-[#111111]">
						
						{/* Pillars */}
						<section class="p-8 hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
							<h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-black tracking-[0.2em] text-white uppercase mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
								<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#d5338b]"></span>
								3 Pilares
							</h3>
							<ul class="space-y-6">
								<li class="p-4 border-[1.5px] border-white/10 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
									<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">1. Desarrollo de Habilidades</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Herramientas y metodologías aplicadas sin distracciones.</p>
								</li>
								<li class="p-4 border-[1.5px] border-white/10 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
									<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">2. Evolución de Proyectos</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Resolviendo problemas en interfaces y backends al instante.</p>
								</li>
								<li class="p-4 border-[1.5px] border-white/10 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
									<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">3. Cero Promesas Vacías</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Progreso documentado sin humo empresarial. Disciplina brutal.</p>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</section>

						{/* Stack Info */}
						<section class="p-8 hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
							<h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-black tracking-[0.2em] text-white uppercase mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
								<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#FAFF00]"></span>
								Armamento
							</h3>
							
							<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
								{['React', 'Tailwind', 'Astro', 'TypeScript', 'Node.js', 'Express', 'PostgreSQL'].map(tech => (
									<span class="px-2 py-1 border-[1.5px] border-white/10 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-300 bg-white/5">
										{tech}
									</span>
								))}
							</div>
							
							<div class="h-[1.5px] w-full bg-white/10 mb-6"></div>

							<p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
								También diseño en el ecosistema <strong>Adobe (Ps, Ai, Ae) y Figma.</strong> He transformado interfaces desde dashboards para bots de Discord hasta infraestructuras complejas para Startups Web.
							</p>
						</section>

						{/* Audience target */}
						<section class="p-8 bg-[#d5338b] text-white">
							<h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-black tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 text-[#0A0A0A]">
								/// PARA QUIÉN ES ESTO
							</h3>
							<p class="text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed drop-shadow-md">
								Gente autodidacta buscando independencia. Personas que necesitan referentes reales, no gurús. Aquí transmitimos control intelectual a través de demostraciones con trabajo puro.
							</p>
						</section>
						
					</div>
				</div>
			</main>

			{/* ── FOOTER ── */}
			<footer class="bg-[#111111]">
				<div class="p-8 md:p-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center border-b-[1.5px] border-white/10 group">
					<span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">¿Tienes una idea en mente?</span>
					<a href="https://zeew.space" target="_blank" class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-zinc-600 hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
						HABLEMOS.
					</a>
				</div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 divide-y-[1.5px] md:divide-y-0 md:divide-x-[1.5px] divide-white/10 text-center">
					<div class="p-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
						<span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-green-500 shadow-[0_0_12px_#22c55e]"></span>
						<span class="font-mono text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-white">Disponible</span>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center justify-center">
						<a href="https://github.com/KamerrEzz" target="_blank" class="font-mono text-[10px] lg:text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub</a>
						<span class="text-zinc-600">/</span>
						<a href="https://linkedin.com/in/KamerrEzz" target="_blank" class="font-mono text-[10px] lg:text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 flex items-center justify-center">
						<span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 tracking-widest uppercase">© {new Date().getFullYear()} KamerrEzz</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</footer>
			
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
